hq qLD5 hq h o1a h hkh kh hkh h o1b h hb gA bA gA hb h o2a h ibpm h o2a h hq qD hq h o1a h hkv kv hkv 
h o1b h hb gA bA gA hb h o2a h ion_pump h o2a h  
# Second cell 
hq qF hq h o1a h hkh kh hkh h o1b h hb gA bA gA hb h o2a h ibpm h o2a h hq qD hq h o1a h hkv kv hkv 
h o1b h hb gA bA gA hb h o2a h ion_pump h o2a h 
# Third cell   
hq qF hq h o1a h hkh kh hkh h o1b h hb gA bA gA hb h o2a h ibpm h o2a h hq qD hq h o1a h hkv kv hkv 
h o1b h hb gA bA gA hb h o2a h ion_pump h o2a h 
# Fourth cell   
hq qF hq h o1a h hkh kh hkh h o1b h hb gA bA gA hb h o2a h ibpm h o2a h hq qD hq h o1a h hkv kv hkv 
h o1b h hb gA bA gA hb h o2a h ion_pump h o2a h 
# straight   
# First cell    
hq qF hq h o1a h hkh kh hkh h o1b oS1 o2a h ibpm h o2a h hq qD hq h o1a h hb_DFK 
gb_DFK1 b_DFK gb_DFK2 hb_DFK h oS1e o2a h 
hb_DSK gb_DSK1 b_DSK gb_DSK2 hb_DSK 
h o1b3 h hb_DSC gb_DSC1 b_DSC gb_DSC2 hb_DSC h o2ab h    
# Second cell    
hb_b_qFd gb_qF1d bqFd gb_qF2d hb_b_qFd h o1a okh oS1b hb_Ld gb_L1d 
bLd gb_L2d hb_Ld h oS1d h     
# d Line 
hq qD hq h odl1 h hb gA bA gA hb h odl1 h hb gA bA gA hb h odl1 h hq qF hq h odl1 h hb gA bA gA hb h 
odl1 h hq qD hq h odl1 h hb gA bA gA hb h odl1 h hq qF hq h odl1 odl1 odl1 h hq qD hq h odl2 h 
hbsweep gbsweep bsweep gbsweep hbsweep h odl3 h od 
end lattice    
